text: Iris Jane Mouzer (born 1937), is a female former athlete who competed for England. ==Athletics career== She represented England in the shot put at the 1958 British Empire and Commonwealth Games in Cardiff, Wales. ==References== Category:1937 births Category:English female shot putters Category:Athletes (track and field) at the 1958 British Empire and Commonwealth Games Category:Living people
title: Iris Mouzer
